There are all of 8 forums where you may want to get into a discussion on some subject.<br>
<br>
Normally, if its a simple question about something, the solution is found on another forum, the thread here locked, and a link to the solution posted.  If a discussion you are engaged in is moved, check the most logical forum, its likely there <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
