<br>
Subjects that are of a more general nature, that discuss things in general, or are discussing ANOTHER class...that can stay in general, at least until it gets into a discussion on class balance.  Then itll be there.<br>
<br>
The forums are not that hard to click on if you are looking for a discussion.  They are kept split up so you can find something that appeals to you, AND find info you need.  Even when the Mage Compendium was 100% updated, people STILL posted many questions here on the general forum.<br>
<br>
ITs just that many dont seem to be used to it.  Balanz is a highly active moderator, which is good.  Some forum mods in places are highly active.  Some forums, the mods dont do much, if anything at all.  Depends on the mods, and the general mood of the forum.<br>
